        "created_at": "2021-07-24T02:45:27.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>wish I had found this producer long ago. Absolutely riveting wine. Can a nose smell thick?  Great density on palate, layers of flavor, super citrus and orchard fruits, very concentrated but lithe, finishes so long and clean. Lemon, lime, peach, all clean and integrated, glycerol-like texture, exceeds expectations. Superb.</p>",
