        "created_at": "2021-07-25T21:09:21.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>The whites are exceptional from Moreau.  I buy the reds every vintage and this particular bottling in many vintages. Wished I could afford the Chevalier in every vintage.  That is a wow wine.  I love this one.  Thanks for the note Alan.</p>",
